quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  41,1,H M
  41,2,"Descent from the merciful, the most merciful"
  41,3,"A Book its verses were detailed/explained/clarified, an Arabic Koran to a nation reasoning/comprehending/knowing"
  41,4,"An announcer of good news and a warner/giver of notice , so most of them objected/opposed , so they do not hear/listen"
  41,5,"And they said: \"Our hearts/minds (are) in covers/protections from what you call us to it, and in our ears (is a) weight/deafness , and from between us and between you (is) a divider/partition , so make/do , that we truly are making/doing"
  41,6,"Say: \"But/truly I am a human equal/alike to you (it) is being transmitted/revealed to me that your Lord (is) one God, so be straight/direct to Him, and ask Him for forgiveness, and calamity/Hell to the sharers/takers of partners (with God)"
  41,7,"Those who do not give/bring the charity/purification , and they are with the end (other life), they are disbelieving"
  41,8,"That truly those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds, for them (is) a reward/wage not interrupted/weakened (continuous)"